videos.description: Al Horford swats Kyle Kuzma's dunk attempt, but the Thunder can't capitalize as the Lakers find a way to get the ball back to Kuzma for a fast-break dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kuzma comes back strong after being blocked by Horford) 2021/02/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kuzma comes back strong after being blocked by Horford

videos.description: After some careless passing, Talen Horton-Tucker tosses an alley-oop up to LeBron James for the easy dunk inside.

videos.description: The Lakers go to overtime against the Thunder as LeBron James knocks down a 3-pointer late in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: LeBron drains a 3 to send Lakers to OT vs. Thunder

videos.description: LeBron James disrupts the inbound pass and the Thunder fail to get off a good shot as the Lakers come away with a 114-113 overtime win.
